txt.en: Hobnanigans is a treasured pastime of the hobbits from the Shire. They have brought the unique game to the festival grounds north of Bree. What could possibly go wrong when you give a dozen adventurers sticks and put a chicken in the middle?

Hobnanigans is a treasured pastime of the hobbits from the Shire. They have brought the unique game to the festival grounds north of Bree. What could possibly go wrong when you give a dozen adventurers sticks and put a chicken in the middle?
Visit the Hobnanigans Fields and attempt to put a chicken through a goal by hitting it with a stick!
Complete to receive a map to the Hobnanigans Fields!
